.TH "__ssp_update_div" 9 "__ssp_update_div" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
__ssp_update_div \- calculate the divisor setting by the line rate
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" __ssp_update_div
.BI "(struct sifive_serial_port *ssp "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ssp" 12
pointer to a struct sifive_serial_port
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Calculate the appropriate value of the clock divisor for the UART
and target line rate referred to by \fIssp\fP and write it into the
hardware.
